code: @Override protected CompletableFuture<JobIdsWithStatusOverview> handleRequest(@Nonnull HandlerRequest<EmptyRequestBody, EmptyMessageParameters> request, @Nonnull RestfulGateway gateway) throws RestHandlerException {     return gateway.requestMultipleJobDetails(timeout).thenApply(multipleJobDetails -> new JobIdsWithStatusOverview(multipleJobDetails.getJobs().stream().map(jobDetails -> new JobIdsWithStatusOverview.JobIdWithStatus(jobDetails.getJobId(), jobDetails.getStatus())).collect(Collectors.toList()))). }
